{"tid":1445941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖 集思廣益)警犬新招搞到好多手足被捕","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:48:10.000Z","uid":299254,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0e3383ad41530bb1abbc436383afef7689875f","tid":1445941,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzH3Lhu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzH3Lhu.jpg&h=5add008a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n今日好多狗混入黑衫搞到手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地除左全身黑衫有埋豬咀眼罩同頭盔<br />\n<br />\n唔係分化狗 即使俾人屌都要出聲<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔預左俾人屌老母<br />\n<br />\n自問只係和理非唔係勇武好廢好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n會唔會諗下轉dress code之類<br />\n<br />\n或者有無其他方法防佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足越捉越小<br />\n<br />\n第一次開po唔知開唔開岩台<br />\n<br />\n如果唔岩幫幫手轉台推<br />\n<br />\n麻煩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰　</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e77742b7a2decfb54e80515c519d3070c900473","tid":1445941,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:37:05.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc2f1ab9004f0ceba98f040b8617becd7b79a8","tid":1445941,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40c0d0baa64d764c6cdf2da0f617c0ae9a09311b","tid":1445941,"uid":299254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Push</spa